  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The followers of this philosophy gain an unmatched power from the shedding of their own blood, one that stokes in others the same burning ardor. Crowds gathered to acclaim the sermons and macabre shows of a Holy guide, are conditioned by it, and can turn into an uncontrollable devastating force capable of taking on reckless enterprises beyond all logic and self-respect. Blood is more powerful than words, but unity can become a cruel and devastating weapon.</span></p>",
